{"tid":913000,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友聲稱處但扑野無血","createTime":"2018-11-23T05:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T07:42:14.000Z","uid":116709,"like":3,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"544c71022e118ad9d0a5182d554e812ca27a4049","tid":913000,"uid":116709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:42:50.000Z","msg":"一齊之前佢有5個bf， 其中兩個拍2yr， 佢聲稱係處但早果排扑野無流血， 話可能細個踩單車穿左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁開頭我都信既but 扑開又覺得鬆鬆地。<br />\n<br />\n 利申非處，扑過ex好緊好緊。<br />\n<br />\n係fb見過佢同ex親密相, kiss果d<br />\n諗起都好酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b5bf990a5d9f6dbea6a459f71a7a35a0ba90ce","tid":913000,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"行過嚟一嘢揸咗落我左邊個mimi度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71651c3740752054de04bc7db9c4d031d07c1efe","tid":913000,"uid":10576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632986dcb611e4805e4aa9cb8fb63bb4c461bb1e","tid":913000,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f33454009ad4f66aa300627d0663bf85c03eb2","tid":913000,"uid":175710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d0b1f0bfe467a19b914e379c6cb87e8346a6f9","tid":913000,"uid":43933,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:47:19.000Z","msg":"人地都冇介意你唔係處啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48847171fec01be6bb057c6ef5e5ba8477c542e","tid":913000,"uid":48624,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"你自己都唔係處 酸乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452264b4e7154aa89008d963fc485e6c842d1f95","tid":913000,"uid":11698,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:54:49.000Z","msg":"我扑左條女4次先破到 但就緊既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16db60bbbc1b99b7deecdb26df3c07052f94980d","tid":913000,"uid":89954,"like":19,"dislike":6,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n<br />\n2. 「性交時有滴血嘅就係處女，無就唔係」？錯！<br />\n有女生係天生就無陰道前膜嘅，就算有，劇烈運動都可以導致陰道前膜破裂。亦有情況係經過多次性交，陰道前膜依然完整。所以，「處女膜」根本不代表什麼。<br />\n<br />\n至於初夜會落紅？其實，約80%女性嘅初夜係沒有肉眼可見嘅出血，可能係因為陰道內膜沒有因性交破裂，亦可能因為破裂嘅位置剛好無血管。就算真係破裂左，多數情況下，亦只會造成前膜多處細小傷痕（而不是坊間想像的「撕裂」或「督穿」佢），出血速度會好慢，同時陰莖插入亦起到壓迫止血嘅作用，所以好少會有明顯嘅血跡。如果好明顯地流血，或有極大痛楚，好可能係因為雙方性經驗或技巧不足，或因緊張等原因，導致陰道未夠濕潤或放鬆，整傷咗陰道組織，並唔係乜嘢值得高興嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n喺古代，多數女孩都係喺青春期結婚，生殖器官未完全成熟，非常脆弱，加上他們不在乎女性嘅需要和舒適，所以更容易會有初夜出血嘅現象，配合視女性為貨物嘅態度，以致流傳左呢種「初夜出血，男人好威」咁嘅錯誤價值觀落黎。<br />\n<br />\n我仲見到世界各地尤其是保守嘅地區，好盛行賣「初夜假血膠囊」或「處女膜封閉手術」，真係荒謬，為嘅就係比女生確保自己與丈夫初次性交時有血，滿足社會嘅要求同丈夫嘅慾望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pikdo.net/p/emiliawyk/1907890457558278296_32356891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpikdo.net%2Fp%2Femiliawyk%2F1907890457558278296_32356891&d=9VGb%2F0e%2BiPoaNMotUy%2Btq0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=d6ed1cd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pikdo.net/p/emiliawyk/1907890457558278296_32356891</a>"},{"pid":"e41f478cfc9c4f38aca6b46d2c74a380b6a56886","tid":913000,"uid":212622,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"452264b4e7154aa89008d963fc485e6c842d1f95","tid":913000,"uid":11698,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:54:49.000Z","msg":"我扑左條女4次先破到 但就緊既<img src=\"/assets/faces/n